# 🧮 Basic Calculator using Python

## 📌 Description:
A command-line calculator that performs basic operations:
- Addition
- Subtraction
- Multiplication
- Division (with zero-division check)

## 💻 How to Run:
Paste and run in Pydroid 3 terminal. Select operations by number and input your values.

